Redis smf and conf files for Solaris. Also a script to download, compile and install it.

./compile

sudo svccfg import redis.smf 
sudo svcadm enable redis
svcs redis

If you are using redis you probably care about:
https://github.com/ezmobius/redis-rb
https://github.com/defunkt/redis-namespace
https://github.com/defunkt/resque
